data.description: Price Ajustment! Make an appointment today to see this beautiful 3/2 split floor plan. This home is great for entertaining inside and outside. The exterior of the home was painted in 2022. The a/c unit was replaced in 2016, water heater and glass sky were replaced in 2023. This home is close to stores, schools and medical facilities. All the wet spaces have tile, and the rooms have laminate floors for easy cleaning. There is an oversized screened in patio and an above ground pool that is fenced in for more privacy. The yard is very spacious for gardening, gatherings or other outdoor hobbies. There is also a 10X12 shed in the yard that can help free up your garage space. Seller will contribute $5k towards buyers closing cost with full price offer. Put in an offer today and get into your new home for the new year!
